The paper describes a competition software for a simulated car racing championship, which involves the use of evolutionary computation and computational intelligence techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Game Theory (cs.GT), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
